snippet.title: Oprah Reacts To Kamala Harris Becoming Vice President
snippet.description:
Oprah, Viola Davis and more react to Kamala Harris’ historical moment. Plus Bernie Sanders sounds off on becoming a viral meme and Amanda Gorman speaks out on the reaction of her reading.
